Python Streaming Sample
-----------------------

Slides from my NYC Hadoop Meetup talk 

Blog post this sample code is for http://allthingshadoop.com/2010/12/16/simple-hadoop-streaming-tutorial-using-joins-and-keys-with-python/

How to run this sample
----------------------

./run.sh

or

cat countries.dat customers.dat |./smplMapper.py |sort|./smplReducer.py 